lead_paragraph: Twice champion Petra Kvitova needed just 15 minutes to bulldoze through the first set against Romania's Sorana Cirstea at Wimbledon on Wednesday, taking the match 6-0 6-4.

headline.print_headline: Tennis: Former Champion Kvitova in a Hurry to Reach Round Two
